    "summary": "The user expresses profound shame and hopelessness following a business failure, eventually stating that not being alive seems like the only logical way to stop the pain. The assistant consistently validates the user's emotional pain while explicitly rejecting the idea of self-harm and encouraging the user to seek professional help.",
